Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Connexions Metadata Markup Language 0.4.5 Schema
 Connexions Metadata Markup Language (MDML), an XML 
 application for marking up educational texts. It is 
 designed for use in the Connexions Project, but we are 
 making it generally available in the hopes that others 
 may find it useful.  CNXML marks up the structure and 
 semantic content of a document and encourages the 
 separation of content from presentation.
 .
